SEC. 20010—ENHANCEMENT OF DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE RESOURCES
FOR IMPROVING THE READINESS OF THE ARMED FORCES
This section provides $11.5 billion in mandatory funding for the
following purposes: to acquire spare parts to keep ships, aircraft,
and land systems mission capable; to modernize and improve the
infrastructure of military depots and shipyards; to acquire addi-
tional capabilities for Special Operation Forces; to improve readi-
