Subtitle D—Pell Grants
Sec. 30031 Eligibility
• Foreign Income. Requires foreign income exempt from taxation
or foreign income for which an individual receives a foreign tax
credit to be included in the AGI calculation for purposes of calcu-
lating Pell Grant eligibility.
