adoption of artificial intelligence models that increase oper-
ational efficiency and service delivery.
(3) To improve, within the Department of Commerce, the cy-
bersecurity posture of Federal information technology systems
through modernized architecture, automated threat detection,
and integrated artificial intelligence solutions.
