law for pharmaceuticals. The Committee remains concerned by the
disincentives to develop cutting-edge medications in the Inflation
Reduction Act. As a result, the Committee is advancing policy that
will make technical corrections to the Inflation Reduction Act and
further incentivize the development of orphan drugs.
