PURPOSE AND SUMMARY
The Committee on the Judiciary’s budget reconciliation provi-
sions provide funding to effectuate President Trump’s immigration
enforcement agenda and creates a series of immigration-related
fees. The Committee’s recommendations also include a series of
funds that will allow the Trump Administration to enact its regu-
latory reform agenda and make agencies more efficient and effec-
tive.
