SEC. 80152. RESCISSION RELATING TO ENVIRONMENTAL
AND CLIMATE DATA COLLECTION.
• Rescinds IRA funding for the Council on Environmental Qual-
ity (CEQ).
• CBO estimates this section will generate up to $25 million in
