the BLM’s Miles City Filed Office in Montana in order to prioritize
coal production over all other considerations. This targets yet an-
other plan developed by the Biden administration designed to sus-
pend future coal leasing in the Powder River Basin in order to re-
duce emissions and promote sustainable land management.
