(a) Subject to subsections (b), (c), and (d) and to section 4304, any
person whose absence from a position of employment is neces-
sitated by reason of service in the uniformed services shall be enti-
tled to the reemployment rights and benefits and other employ-
ment benefits of this chapter if—
